      "content": "it's not even about \"practical steps\" anymore. doctors just give me more pills that make me feel like a zombie but the pain is still there. it feels like there's no real exit. sometimes i just lie here thinking how much easier it would be if everything just... went quiet. if i didn't have to wake up to this every single morning. wouldn't it be a mercy to just have some peace?",
